high_descs: Walk towards the door, then turn right to face the table.
Pick up the butter knife off of the table.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the counter and look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the cabinet door in front of you and put the butter knife in the black cup that is in the cabinet.
Pick up the black cup with the butter knife in it out of the cabinet and then close the door.
Turn right and walk towards the counter, then turn right to face the sink.
Place the black cup with the butter knife in it in the sink behind the golden spoon.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a butter knife in it in the sink.
